snippet.title: Zebulon: A Lost Cat - Trailer
snippet.description:
Zebulon: A Lost Cat is a new tiny platformer metroidvania where you are playing a small cat, the game is coming to Steam and Itch.io on August 5 2024! It was made with pico-8 fantasy console, you can wishlist it on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3047460/Zebulon_A_Lost_Cat
